<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="66" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="66">• Medium-sized prosimians with long hindlimbs, shortish, blunt face, large eyes, prominent, rounded ears, soft, dense, woolly, reddish, brown, and gray fur, and tail not longer than body.</paragraph>
